{"tid":734743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Justin Bieber封盤！向舊愛索模求婚成功","createTime":"2018-07-09T02:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T19:09:51.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ce194c114b935234c1f4ab49bf388ba304fa8053","tid":734743,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"現年24歲加拿大小天王Justin Bieber除咗唱功了得，最出名都要算係佢嘅緋聞，同勁多女星傳過，而且同前女友Selena Gomez離合咗N次，不過呢啲消息都要終止！因為Justin已經訂咗婚，對象就係復合咗兩個月嘅21歲舊愛Hailey Baldwin！ <br />\n<br />\n據美國媒體報道，有目擊者指Justin於美國時間7日晚在巴哈馬度假勝地一間餐廳內求婚成功，當時佢怕走漏消息，叫保鏢收起現場人士嘅手機，仲宣布話轉頭有大事發生，隔咗冇耐，佢就係眾人面前，單膝跪地向女友求婚！ <br />\n<br />\n除咗目擊者爆料之外，睇番雙方家長嘅社交網，佢哋都有留言講呢件事，好似Justin嘅爸爸留言話：「 Proud is an understatement! Excited for the next chapter!（驕傲不足以表達我的感受，為「新一頁」感到開心。）」而Hailey嘅爸爸亦有留言話祝福「JB &amp; HB」，佢仲Tag晒Justin嘅父母！已經通知晒雙方家長，唔知佢哋擇咗日舉行婚禮未呢？"},{"pid":"73212d321aaf3c68ce9976659659aee5d439dc48","tid":734743,"uid":132587,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"原來佢仲係得24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b99e3f71267a29d58c5947e6d338d23140ab331","tid":734743,"uid":165365,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"Shawn Mendes咁快比條女飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2971ee5e413280f2a7175d9b7024345895397fd8","tid":734743,"uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9b99e3f71267a29d58c5947e6d338d23140ab331","tid":734743,"uid":165365,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"Shawn Mendes咁快比條女飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"一齊一陣就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50cb4ce79b48458e0e83a0680851e16ec231d5c","tid":734743,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:2